rows.label: qev097805_MSG0002
rows.name:
Looks like you managed to track down Henahena's
boyfriend.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev097805_MSG0003
rows.name:
You should have seen itâ€”as soon as I told her he'd
come home, she was bursting with energy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev097805_MSG0004
rows.name:
Said she wasn't about to let him see her bedridden,
so she got up and started preening...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev097805_MSG0005
rows.name:
It was sweet. And their big emotional reunion is just
about to happen.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev097805_MSG0007
rows.name: ...Ah, speak of the devil. Here comes Henahena.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev097805_MSG0010
rows.name: Bobora hear news and come running![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev097805_MSG0013
rows.name:
Of course! Bobora here to see Henahena finally
feeling better![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev097805_MSG0014
rows.name:
Oh, Bobora! It has been so, so, SO long!
Henahena missed you so much![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev097805_MSG0019
rows.name: Leaving already? And Bobora only just came home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev097805_MSG0020
rows.name:
Henahena finally better now, but even still,
Bobora is wanderer. Cruel, beautiful wanderer...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev097805_MSG0021
rows.name: Henahena will wait for return of Bobora always.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev097805_MSG0024
rows.name:
Well, it was emotional for a second there, at least.
I guess that's enough?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev097805_MSG0027
rows.name:
So, um... Would you hate me if I asked you to track
him down one more time?[ST:wait ]
